      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Serve the <strong>crispy ham hock</strong> over the <strong>carrot &amp; potato mash</strong> with the <strong>garlicky greens</strong> to the side</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Drizzle the<strong> creamy mustard sauce</strong> all over</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Enjoy!</span></p>",
